# WillyBeat Preset v2
version: 2
name:    Soulful Snare Roll Fill
genres:  Soul, R&B, Funk, Backbeat, Snare Roll, Vintage, Retro, 60s, Classic, Smooth, Groove, Live Drums, Mid-tempo, Fill
